    hook_question_en: 'If a recovery agent says to \'Settle\' the loan by paying half the money, know how much loss you have in this.',
    viz_body: 'Loan ka \'Settlement\' karna aur loan \'Close\' karna do alag batein hain.<br>Settlement karne par aapke CIBIL report mein hamesha ke liye <b>bura nishan (red flag) lag jata hai</b> jisse aage loan milna mushkil hota hai.',
    viz_body_en: 'Doing a loan \'Settlement\' and doing a loan \'Closure\' are two different things.<br>Upon settlement, a <b>bad mark (red flag) stays permanently</b> on your CIBIL report which makes getting future loans difficult.',
    micro_action: 'Hamesha koshish karein ki late fees dekar sahi, par loan ko poori tarah \'Close\' karein aur NOC maangein.',
