    hook_question_en: 'Many people think that checking their CIBIL score repeatedly makes the score drop. This is a complete lie.',
    viz_body: 'Jab aap khud apna score app par check karte hain (Soft Enquiry), toh score par koi asar nahi padta.<br>Score tab girta hai jab aap <b>bahut saare banks mein ek sath naye loan ke liye apply</b> (Hard Enquiry) karte hain.',
