    hook_question: 'Bank mein FD karwane gaye the, aur unhone galti se ek lamba insurance chipka diya. Ab kya karein?',
    hook_question_en: 'Went to the bank to get an FD done, and they mistakenly stuck a long insurance policy. What to do now?',
    viz_body: 'IRDAI ke niyam ke anusaar, har life aur health insurance policy mein \'Free Look Period\' hota hai.<br>Policy documents milne ke <b>15 se 30 din ke andar</b> aap usay cancel karke apna poora paisa wapas le sakte hain.',
    viz_body_en: 'As per IRDAI rules, every life and health insurance policy has a \'Free Look Period\'.<br>Within <b>15 to 30 days</b> of receiving the policy documents, you can cancel it and get all your money back.',
    micro_action: 'Insurance ki kitaab (document) par milne ki tarikh likhein, aur agent ki man-ne ke bajaye turant company ko email karein.',
    micro_action_en: 'Write the receiving date on the insurance book (document), and instead of listening to the agent, email the company immediately.',
