    viz_body_en: 'No, the expenses and bill payments on an Add-on card<br>are only reported to the <b>Primary Cardholder\'s (main account)</b> CIBIL.<br>This does not build any credit history for the person using the Add-on card.',
    micro_action: 'Wife/bacho ki credit history banani ho toh unhe unke khud ke naam par card ya chota loan dilwayein.',
    micro_action_en: 'If you want to build the credit history of your wife/children, get them a card or a small loan in their own name.',
