    hook_question: 'Flat interest rate aur Reducing interest rate mein se konsa loan sasta padta hai?',
    hook_question_en: 'Between Flat interest rate and Reducing interest rate, which loan is cheaper?',
    viz_body: 'Hamesha <b>Reducing interest rate sasta padta hai</b>.<br>Flat rate mein byaaj poore time original amount par lagta hai,<br>jabki Reducing rate mein byaaj sirf utne paise par lagta hai jitna karza bacha hua hai (jo har mahine EMI dene se kam hota hai).',
    viz_body_en: 'The <b>Reducing interest rate is always cheaper</b>.<br>In a flat rate, interest is charged on the original amount for the entire tenure,<br>while in a reducing rate, interest is charged only on the outstanding loan balance (which decreases with every EMI).',
