    id: 'loans-gold-loan-ltv-ratio-01',
    tag_category: 'loans-cibil',
    hook_question: '1 Lakh rupaye ka sona girvi rakhne par bank kitna loan de sakta hai?',
    hook_question_en: 'How much loan can the bank give on pledging gold worth Rs 1 Lakh?',
    viz_body: 'RBI ke niyam anusar, bank sone ki market value ka <b>maximum 75% tak (Loan-to-Value ya LTV ratio)</b> loan de sakte hain.<br>Iska matlab hai 1 Lakh ke sone par aapko zyada se zyada 75,000 rupaye tak ka loan mil sakta hai.',
    viz_body_en: 'As per RBI rules, banks can give a loan up to a <b>maximum of 75% of the gold\'s market value (Loan-to-Value or LTV ratio)</b>.<br>This means on gold worth 1 Lakh, you can get a maximum loan of up to Rs 75,000.',
