    viz_body: 'Legal heir (waris) ko us person ke <b>Assessing Officer (AO) ko ek written letter likhna hota hai</b>.<br>Letter mein maut ka certificate, PAN card ki copy aur surrender karne ki request daal kar Income Tax office mein jama karni hoti hai.',
    viz_body_en: 'The legal heir has to write a <b>written letter to the Assessing Officer (AO) of that person</b>.<br>The letter along with the death certificate, a copy of the PAN card, and a request to surrender must be submitted to the Income Tax office.',
    micro_action: 'Maut ke turant baad PAN surrender na karein, jab tak property aur tax return ke saare kaam poore na ho jayein.',
    micro_action_en: 'Do not surrender the PAN immediately after death until all property and tax return tasks are completed.',
